Job Description:
The functional role requirs day to day management of office premies. Ensures office premises are clean and well managed. Can deal with vendors regrding office improvements and maintaining office infrastructure. All aspects of administartion will be handled by employee. That includes ensuring UPS, Generators are functioning properly and not impeding the office. Any inter connectivity issues that employees face will be taken care of by employee. For office cleanliness there will be staff working under the employee. Strong skills working with people, pro active and engaged, strong negotiation skills and takes the initative.
Skills Required:
, administrative, works well with cross functional teams.
